</list>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm265454224">
<problem id="fs-idm250424336">
<para id="fs-idm252718416"><link class="lo-reference" document="m67836"/>Which of the following is typically required for entry-level positions in the accounting profession?</para>
<list id="fs-idm268147776" list-type="enumerated" number-style="upper-alpha">
